Erika Eleniak https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Erika_Eleniak 0 Erika Eleniak (born September 29, 1969) is an American-Canadian actress, Playboy Playmate, and former model best known for her role in Baywatch as Shauni McClain. Her film debut was a small part in E.T.: The Extra-Terrestrial (1982). She later starred in the films The Blob, Under Siege, and The Beverly Hillbillies.
